title: SHREDDED (2014) - Eric Snaell The Fit Businessman. 2 Superfoods
description:
Eric Snaell the Fit Businessman presents 
SHREDDED - 2 SUPER FOODS AND 2 EXERCISES

Brief booklet showing two recommended meals and two recommended exercises that any businessman or businesswoman can easily add to their healthy lifestyle. Anyone familiar with the fitness channel on Youtube (ExplosiveMode.com) will know what to expect. It's all about getting SHREDDED even if you have kids and a full-time job.
